I"à<p>Above you can see how it looks like.</p>

<p>To enable it add a <code class="highlighter-rouge">toc</code> variable to the front matter of your post:</p>

<figure class="highlight"><pre><code class="language-md" data-lang="md">layout: post
title: Table of content
date:   2018-08-03 11:07
description: For some big articles you can use table on content
toc: true           &lt;=========== this one</code></pre></figure>

<p>You can also customize it by styling <code class="highlighter-rouge">.toc</code> class in <strong>theme.scss</strong></p>

<p>This solution is based on <a href="https://github.com/allejo/jekyll-toc">github.com/allejo/jekyll-toc</a>.</p>

